---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseHead title={`FIPS 140-3 Level 3 Encrypted Drives | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Eliminate data breach risk from lost devices. The iStorage datAshur Pro2+ delivers FIPS 140-3 Level 3 certified hardware encryption for NZ businesses." />

<Header />
<main>
	<!-- HERO: Lead with the PAIN -->
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Your Data Shouldn't Be This Vulnerable</h1>
			<p class="tagline">A lost laptop or USB drive shouldn't mean a million-dollar data breach. Secure your physical data with the highest certified hardware encryption available.</p>
			<a href="/consultation" class="btn primary">Get a Free Security Assessment</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="products-content">
		<div class="container">

			<!-- THE SINGLE, FOCUSED SOLUTION -->
			<section class="core-offering">
				<h2>Our Exclusive Recommendation: FIPS 140-3 Level 3 Encryption</h2>
				<p>After extensive evaluation of the certified security market, we recommend one product that stands above the rest for maximum physical data protection.</p>

				<div class="product-showcase">
					<div class="product-card featured">
						<div class="featured-badge">Our Top Pick</div>
						<h3>iStorage datAshur Pro +C</h3>
						<p class="product-subtitle">FIPS 140-3 Level 3 Certified • The Highest Commercial Assurance Available</p>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>FIPS 140-3 Level 3 Certified</strong> - Beyond military-grade to tamper-proof physical security</li>
							<li><strong>Brute-Force Proof Protection</strong> - Permanently locks after 20 failed PIN attempts with cryptographic erasure</li>
							<li><strong>Zero Software Dependencies</strong> - Works instantly on any system without admin rights or drivers</li>
							<li><strong>Built-in Keypad & AES 256-bit Encryption</strong> - All data encrypted on the device before leaving</li>
							<li><strong>Time-Based Auto-Lock</strong> - Configurable inactivity locking for operational security</li>
							<li><strong>Independent Secure Operation</strong> - The host computer is completely untrusted</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="procurement-note">
							<strong>Why We Recommend This:</strong> After testing the market, the datAshur Pro +C represents the pinnacle of certified hardware encryption. We specify and source this product through authorized channels for clients who require uncompromising data protection.
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- WHY THIS CERTIFICATION MATTERS -->
			<section class="certification-explainer">
				<h2>Why FIPS 140-3 Level 3 is the Gold Standard</h2>
				<div class="cert-grid">
					<div class="cert-point">
						<h3>Tamper-Proof Physical Security</h3>
						<p>Level 3 certification requires active tamper detection and response. Any physical intrusion attempt triggers immediate cryptographic erasure.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="cert-point">
						<h3>Beyond Software Encryption</h3>
						<p>Software solutions like BitLocker rely on the host computer's security. Hardware encryption operates independently in a trusted environment.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="cert-point">
						<h3>Independently Verified</h3>
						<p>FIPS certification means the encryption module has been rigorously tested and validated by government-accredited laboratories.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- THE PROCESS: How We Deliver This -->
			<section class="our-process">
				<h2>We Don't Just Recommend Hardware. We Deliver Complete Security.</h2>
				<div class="process-steps">
					<div class="step">
						<h3>1. Assess & Specify</h3>
						<p>We perform a <strong>OPSEC Health Check</strong> to determine if the datAshur Pro2+ is the right solution for your specific data protection needs.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<h3>2. Source & Configure</h3>
						<p>We procure through authorized channels and pre-configure devices with your security policies before deployment.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<h3>3. Deploy & Train</h3>
						<p>We ensure your team understands how to properly use the devices, integrating hardware into your security practices.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- THE URGENT CTA -->
			<section class="client-cta">
				<h2>Stop Compromising on Data Security</h2>
				<p>When your data demands the highest level of protection, settle for nothing less than certified assurance.</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<a href="/consultation" class="btn primary">Get Your Free Threat Assessment</a>
					<a href="mailto:contact@hermetrix.nz?subject=datAshur Pro2+ Inquiry" class="btn secondary">Ask About Certified Hardware</a>
				</div>
			</section>

		</div>
	</section>

</main>
<Footer />

<style>
body {
	margin: 0;
	min-height: 100vh;
	font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
	line-height: 1.6;
	background: #f8fafc;
}

main {
	flex: 1;
}

/* Hero Section */
.hero {
	padding: 4rem 0;
	text-align: center;
	background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1419 0%, #1a365d 50%, #2d3748 100%);
	color: white;
	position: relative;
	overflow: hidden;
	width: 100vw;
	margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
}
.hero > .container {
	position: relative;
	z-index: 1;
	padding: 0 2rem;
}
.hero h1 {
	font-size: 3.2rem;
	margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	font-weight: 900;
	color: #ffffff;
	text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
	letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}
.tagline {
	font-size: 1.5rem;
	font-weight: 400;
	margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	color: #90cdf4;
	max-width: 700px;
	margin-left: auto;
	margin-right: auto;
}

/* Products Content */
.products-content {
	padding: 5rem 1rem;
	background: #f8fafc;
}
.container {
	max-width: 1200px;
	margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Core Offering */
.core-offering {
	margin-bottom: 5rem;
	text-align: center;
}
.core-offering h2 {
	font-size: 2.5rem;
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
	color: #0f1419;
}
.core-offering > p {
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	max-width: 800px;
	margin: 0 auto 3rem;
	color: #4a5568;
}

.product-showcase {
	display: flex;
	justify-content: center;
	margin-top: 3rem;
}
.product-card {
	background: white;
	padding: 3rem;
	border-radius: 0.75rem;
	border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
	box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,54,93,0.12);
	text-align: left;
	max-width: 900px;
	width: 100%;
	position: relative;
}
.product-card.featured {
	border: 2px solid #3182ce;
	box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(49, 130, 206, 0.15);
}
.featured-badge {
	position: absolute;
	top: -12px;
	left: 50%;
	transform: translateX(-50%);
	background: #3182ce;
	color: white;
	padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
	border-radius: 2rem;
	font-weight: 700;
	font-size: 0.9rem;
	text-transform: uppercase;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}
.product-card h3 {
	color: #1a365d;
	margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	font-size: 1.8rem;
	text-align: center;
}
.product-subtitle {
	color: #718096;
	font-style: italic;
	margin-bottom: 2rem;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	text-align: center;
}
.product-card ul {
	margin: 1.5rem 0;
	padding-left: 0;
	list-style: none;
}
.product-card li {
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
	padding-left: 1.5rem;
	position: relative;
}
.product-card li:before {
	content: "✓";
	color: #38a169;
	font-weight: bold;
	position: absolute;
	left: 0;
}
.procurement-note {
	background: #f0f9ff;
	border: 1px solid #bee3f8;
	border-left: 4px solid #3182ce;
	padding: 1.5rem;
	border-radius: 0.5rem;
	margin-top: 2rem;
	font-size: 1rem;
	color: #2d3748;
	line-height: 1.6;
}
.procurement-note strong {
	color: #2b6cb0;
}

/* Certification Explainer */
.certification-explainer {
	margin-bottom: 5rem;
	text-align: center;
}
.certification-explainer h2 {
	font-size: 2.2rem;
	margin-bottom: 3rem;
	color: #0f1419;
}
.cert-grid {
	display: grid;
	grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
	gap: 2rem;
}
.cert-point {
	background: white;
	padding: 2rem;
	border-radius: 0.5rem;
	border-top: 4px solid #3182ce;
	box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
	text-align: left;
}
.cert-point h3 {
	color: #1a365d;
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
}

/* Process Section */
.our-process {
	margin-bottom: 5rem;
	text-align: center;
}
.our-process h2 {
	font-size: 2.2rem;
	margin-bottom: 3rem;
	color: #0f1419;
}
.process-steps {
	display: grid;
	grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
	gap: 2rem;
}
.step {
	background: white;
	padding: 2rem;
	border-radius: 0.5rem;
	border-top: 4px solid #3182ce;
	box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}
.step h3 {
	color: #1a365d;
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* Client CTA */
.client-cta {
	background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a365d 0%, #2d3748 100%);
	color: white;
	padding: 4rem 2rem;
	border-radius: 1rem;
	text-align: center;
	margin-bottom: 3rem;
}
.client-cta h2 {
	font-size: 2.5rem;
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.client-cta p {
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	margin-bottom: 2rem;
	opacity: 0.9;
}
.cta-buttons {
	display: flex;
	gap: 1rem;
	justify-content: center;
	flex-wrap: wrap;
}

/* Buttons */
.btn {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  text-align: center;
  border: 2px solid transparent;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}
.btn.primary {
  background-color: #90cdf4;
  color: #1a365d;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(144, 205, 244, 0.4);
}
.btn.primary:hover {
  background-color: #63b3ed;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(144, 205, 244, 0.6);
}
.btn.secondary {
  background-color: transparent;
  color: #90cdf4;
  border: 2px solid #90cdf4;
}
.btn.secondary:hover {
  background-color: rgba(144, 205, 244, 0.1);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  .tagline { font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .product-card { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
  .cta-buttons { flex-direction: column; }
  .btn { width: 100%; }
  .cert-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .hero { padding: 3rem 1rem; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
  .product-card { padding: 1.5rem 1rem; }
  .core-offering h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
  .featured-badge { font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.4rem 1rem; }
}
</style>